00:09:57,531 --> 00:10:00,331
"Yuri Saeki (30), Asisten Nagisa"

137
00:10:00,331 --> 00:10:02,231
Apel itu untuk apa?

138
00:10:02,231 --> 00:10:06,931
Dia selalu menyuruh Nagisa mengupas apel untuk membuatnya tenang.

139
00:10:06,931 --> 00:10:09,831
Kalau kupasannya pendek, dia masih gugup.

140
00:10:09,831 --> 00:10:13,731
